      "title": "The 2-modular reduction of the Steinberg representation of a finite Chevalley group of type C n",
      "abstract": "Abstract We show that, in characteristic 2, the Steinberg representation of the symplectic group Sp2n(q), for q a power of an odd prime p, has two irreducible constituents, lying just above the socle, which are isomorphic to the two Weil modules of degree ."
